Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:43.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}貴方は風のように 目を閉じては夕暮れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:49.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何を思っているんだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:02.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目蓋を開いていた 貴方の目はビイドロ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:09.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}少しだけ晴るの匂いがした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:20.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴れに晴れ、花よ咲け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:24.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}咲いて晴るのせい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:29.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}降り止めば雨でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:34.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}貴方を飾る晴る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:39.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}胸を打つ音よ凪げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:43.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕ら晴る風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}あの雲も越えてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:52.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}遠くまだ遠くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:43.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你像风儿一样 闭上双眼却是黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:49.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}此刻你究竟在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:02.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}望向远方的你 眼眸好似彩色琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:09.14,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}让人感到些许 晴天味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:20.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴日春又晴 花儿盛放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:24.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}花开怪春晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:29.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}春晴风渐和 雨也是晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:34.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}点点洒落你身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:39.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}胸中的浪涛 快快平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:43.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们好似晴风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}要吹过天际的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:52.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}去最遥远的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And I'm alright (I'll be alright)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Yeah I hear you (I care about you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:01.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:13.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかったものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どうして 溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}せめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}会いたいよ なんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ねえ　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:37.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今日だけは 思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:43.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}あなたとまた巡りあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:48.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう迷わない 今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑って見せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目を閉じれば いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつでも届いているから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:19.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I'm whispering our lullaby by for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我一切都好(我会好的)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是 我听得到(我想念你)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:01.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}风儿缠绕着你变长的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}一切的一切都有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就连那些止步不前的日子也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:13.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算知道迟了 我也追上了你的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}看 如果不是这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.54,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就看不见的那些事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}为什么 会充盈眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.46,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}起码
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我不会说出想要见你之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:37.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}至少今天 我可以思念你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:43.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}倘若能和你再度邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:48.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我不会再犹豫 一定会选择当下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}让我看到笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要闭上双眼 就一直
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便我们间从没有绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们也早就心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}流下泪水也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}长夜定会迎来黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:19.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我轻声吟唱着摇篮曲 期盼你能归来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.51,0:24:29.71,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\1c&HDEE5E2&}那下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fsp5.5\fad(0,0)\pos(1428,933)}人类的时代
